article.description: — Tevin Brewer had 19 points as Florida International got past Marshall 70-64 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Brewer, Hawkins lead FIU past Marshall 70-64
article.linkText: Brewer, Hawkins lead FIU past Marshall 70-64
article.story: MIAMI -- — Tevin Brewer had 19 points as Florida International got past Marshall 70-64 on Thursday night. Javaunte Hawkins added 17 points, Clevon Brown had 16 points and 11 rebounds, and Seth Pinkney had three blocks for FIU (11-7, 1-4 Conference USA). Taevion Kinsey had 25 points and six rebounds for the Thundering Herd (7-11, 0-5), whose losing streak stretched to eight games. Andrew Taylor added 13 points and Obinna Anochili-Killen had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
